import sys
input = sys.stdin.readline
num_test_cases = int(input())
for test_case_ittr in range(num_test_cases):
    (length, target) = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
    possible = False
    for candidate_min in range(1, length + 1):
        (subarray_length, mod) = divmod(target, candidate_min)
        if mod == 0 and subarray_length <= length - candidate_min + 1:
            possible = True
            break
    print('YES' if possible else 'NO')
